Description:
DESCRIPTION

PaWz Massager is an ideal solution for your pets to release fatigue or tension effectively.  Apart from muscle relieve for neck, arms, back, legs it helps pet to relieve itchiness. Clockwise / anti-clockwise rotation with two speed levels to choose a desire speed for target area. 4 massage heads with 76 massage points, wet or dry use available. Widely cover acupoints and provide a comfortable pressing, both human and pet friendly. Detachable massage head for easy cleaning. Furthermore, it comes with a USB interface for convenient charging. Lightweight yet silent operation, use it anywhere as you like.
